Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“年轻人 为何徘徊于此”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我在寻找着阳光 却迷失了方向”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多用丹田发声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让声音能穿越这油泥海到达对岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能传得到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是开开心心搞文化节的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台词都已经倒背如流了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.83,0:02:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来问题出在这手上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得交臂的时候 你总被我先抓住领子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.60,0:02:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“追寻阳光却为何来到这不见天日的森林?”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好迟呀 明之 而且那是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚要出门 我老妈就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许找借口 你的角色一直都是古市在顶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手张开给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只手也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“然后这名老翁便抓住年轻人的双手”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“试起了他的腕力”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“然而影子却是因阳光而生的”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把别人压在自己的阴影下 感觉很不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市 你…被希洛克…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.64,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校车爆炸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实在那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被选中了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止我是怀着什么样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 该由我来给你安排角色了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧 别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之 你想法使女人远离那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个扎穆德已经迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个希洛克因为憎恨而进化了 没救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退远点好好看着吧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底谁是光 谁是影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的眼睛确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是只用憎恨喂食希洛克的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.99,0:04:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 你会被希洛克的怨恨所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去的话就说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…想…活…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 已经连扎穆德的面貌都失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得刚才有点火大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干嘛非得祈求那家伙不可?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫不懂人情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.16,0:04:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我心情舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是你的敌人吧 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该说你的敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.41,0:05:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.45,0:05:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生气了 古市 快给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 当影子要更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漆黑的夜里 谁都找不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么呼喊 都不会有人来找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是从什么时候开始的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始觉得阳光太耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 是自从遇到了你以后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这都已经没关系了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.16,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今往后 我会成为光 这家伙才是影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 有件事你要明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢明之
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.85,0:06:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春 连你也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜次上这样一个无聊的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生一个随处可见的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阴郁又无聊的日子里 找到点微不足道的幸福就满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你所期望的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说你是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明就没真正喜欢过一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你知不知道这很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然被这种小狐狸精迷住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太不谨慎了 小明之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 真是的 怎么能随便跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚醒来的春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么处置那家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法 谁让他这么耀眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光也好影也好 古市就是古市 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成不了光的话 还怎么照耀你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我也能成为像你一样的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 说“是”吧 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是在那时候被选中的人 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.60,0:08:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你安静点行不行 快点去死行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 那个女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要藏好了 春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩远走高飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都搞错了 这世界太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话 就无法救回那个女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能杀了他了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.34,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寻找着阳光…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却迷失了…方向…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要迷失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则你自己也会回不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过于庞大的憎恨阻碍了石化吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你真是个傻瓜 古市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 感觉轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.12,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会恢复原样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以找龙藏医生商量一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会像以前一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个人就像以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候怎么就不下场雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晴朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空 蓝得过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认命中 对象停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各机 发射实弹须经许可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ASP是用来守护这个岛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知这样 我才不会当什么主魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我认为这也是在守护这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 不会杀他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有不少事情需要这两位帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:13:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 应该说“这两只”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,己方人员中居然会有扎穆德诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次欢迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是犯人 不会对她动粗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉打扰你的重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有不少事情要问你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.99,0:13:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢藏小秘密的西村春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿到我的房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:13:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 请带上面罩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 怪闷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.84,0:14:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 您是说这怪物吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.18,0:14:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有一个女人 把她找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该…怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 娜琪亚美
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才把你丢出去 很疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回港口去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还得回故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没赶来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.12,0:14:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要犹豫 让他们立即开船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会追上来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是赶不上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在赞巴尼号上等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.77,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 在后面 后面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急着开火
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确保中佐的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.62,0:15:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我把中佐放开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动 快松手 你这怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我疏忽大意 咎由自取
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当我已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.59,0:15:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么… 中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要给扎穆德致命的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓活的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不快开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下不了手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说这些没经历过战争的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特务编队紧急呼叫第7区及其周边各人员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,01号监视目标 竹原明之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挟持垣巢中佐后逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 带着中佐逃跑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽大意 万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的收容准备刚完成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 市区周边已部署了重装警队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外围ASP也正在展开中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将西村春和寺冈古市分开送往这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可能会有与扎穆德接触的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.49,0:16:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待中佐的表现吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对扎穆德究竟会说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候越是无知的人越容易抓住真相呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我有点困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:16:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底该如何跟你交流
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白我的话吗 竹原明之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我的性命总是辗转于你们父子手中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我老爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲是我的战友 同时也是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能冷静的跟你谈几句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能把手松开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会加害春和古市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两人对我而言都是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能给你们安排一个生存的空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一个泰斯克的少女曾跟你在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能告诉我更多关于你们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪力 骨折了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经发现垣巢中佐 己经发现垣巢中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹原明之目前依然在逃亡中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护送车3号 1号 报告现在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护送车1号 现在正通过商店街
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号骨骼呼叫1号
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现对象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 三分钟左右会合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达前不要开火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下来 停下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要动 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1号骨骼呼叫2号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在位置是北面8加普
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.70,0:19:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我开火了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.21,0:19:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 你在干什么 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.88,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.54,0:19:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太恶心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 好迟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你好受的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐真生气的时候 可是很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.39,0:19:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,载着古市的护送车失去联系了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙可能去的地方 或者值得留恋的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么呢 阿婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿好像抽筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我三瓶冰镇的弹珠汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等会儿 我去给你把冰得最透的拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人喝得了那么多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当心得蛀牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瓶是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瓶是给最爱的春
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一瓶就给我最…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.81,0:20:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抵抗的话 就不会杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 大家直到最后都要多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面容也好 生命也好…都是因为会消逝才显得美丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.82,0:21:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连可以入土为安的故乡都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.41,0:21:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说 我真不明白你们的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.87,0:21:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.37,0:21:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还未成年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定这时候那些家伙也在什么地方仰望这轮明月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪越大就越不想动了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你能从坟墓里爬起来 往我后面踹上一脚?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起来 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明 明…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙搞什么 连话都不会说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.08,0:22:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁捡来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.92,0:22:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字…是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.56,0:24:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个难叫醒的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.44,0:24:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个漂泊在北国的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人偶然相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.94,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡不醒的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行于雪国的愁苦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.95,0:24:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价实在太高了





